IMPORTANT NEWS EVERYBODY
it seems that a scan group of the name of "Karam scans" has made a tl of Komen Fuufu, despite the ones made by anon here already being on mangadex
Most of you aren't weebs so you probably aren't familiar with this, but in the manga community this is known as "snipping" or something like that
Basically it's when a group starts translating a manga despite another group/person already doing it
This can happen for a lot of reasons, with the most common being that the original team isn't translating anymore new chapters, or the translation just isn't good and the other team thinks they can do better
Now this could result in two things:
>1. The anon who did the original 8 chapters will come back to release more, telling the new team to basically leave his territory
>2. The anon does absolutely nothing, and let this probably more experienced team just handle it
No offense to the anon who originally translated Komen Fuufu at all, btw, but it does seem that the new team is a bit of a higher quality
